OL,3,CFewer medical staff stay in Wales
OL,4,Cafter qualifying compared to rest of
OL,5,Cthe UK
OL,7,FThe NHS in Wales is still seriously
OL,8,Fstruggling with recruiting and
OL,9,Fretaining staff according to a new
OL,10,Freport by Audit Wales.
OL,12,FAs a result health boards are still
OL,13,Frelying on expensive agency staff
OL,14,Fleading to calls for urgent collective
OL,15,Faction to address the problem.
OL,17,F- NHS staff costs increased by 62%
OL,18,Ffrom #3.23 billion in 2017-18 to #5.23
OL,19,Fbillion in 2023-24
