OL,3,CFewer medical staff stay in Wales
OL,4,Cafter qualifying compared to rest of
OL,5,Cthe UK
OL,7,F- 1 in 10 medical and dental posts are
OL,8,Fcurrently vacant.
OL,10,F- Of the 8,180 doctors currently on
OL,11,Fthe General Medical Council register
OL,12,Fwho originally trained in Wales, only
OL,13,F42.8% (3,505) have remained in Wales
OL,15,FWhen compared with the other home
OL,16,Fnations, England retains 94% of
OL,17,Fdoctors who train there, Scotland
OL,18,Fretains 61% and Northern Ireland keeps
OL,19,F76%
