OL,3,CFewer medical staff stay in Wales
OL,4,Cafter qualifying compared to rest of
OL,5,Cthe UK
OL,7,FSince 2017-18 NHS staffing costs have
OL,8,Fgrown by 62%, however in the current
OL,9,Fclimate, there are worries that this
OL,10,Fis not sustainable.
OL,12,FThe report published today also notes
OL,13,Fpositive progress with the size of the
OL,14,FNHS workforce growing to cope with the
OL,15,Fincreasing demands.
OL,17,FOther areas which showed positive
OL,18,Fdevelopments are sickness absence
OL,19,Fmanagement and reducing agency staff.
