OL,3,CFewer medical staff stay in Wales
OL,4,Cafter qualifying compared to rest of
OL,5,Cthe UK
OL,7,FAudit Wales says NHS Wales "needs to
OL,8,Fadapt to the changing demand it is
OL,9,Ffacing."
OL,11,FThey added "Workforce planning can't
OL,12,Fbe undertaken in isolation.
OL,14,F"The Welsh Government needs to work
OL,15,Fwith senior leaders in NHS Wales and
OL,16,Fkey partners to address these issues
OL,17,Fby developing a longer-term workforce
OL,18,Fplan."
