OL,3,CFewer medical staff stay in Wales
OL,4,Cafter qualifying compared to rest of
OL,5,Cthe UK
OL,7,FAudit Wales highlights that the plan
OL,8,Fshould focus on ensuring staff who are
OL,9,Ftrained in Wales remain in Wales. This
OL,10,Fissue was highlighted in a BMA Cymru
OL,11,Fsurvey from last year, 2024, which
OL,12,Frevealed 39% of medical students plan
OL,13,Fto leave Wales after graduation to
OL,14,Fstart their medical careers elsewhere.
OL,15,FThe main reasons given by these
OL,16,Fstudents for wanting to leave was for
OL,17,Fbetter pay and better working
OL,18,Fconditions.
