OL,7,FA Welsh Government spokesperson has
OL,8,Fsaid "The NHS in Wales now has more
OL,9,Fstaff than at any point in its
OL,10,Fhistory, directly employing almost
OL,11,F97,000 full time equivalent staff ` a
OL,12,F21% increase since before the pandemic.
OL,14,F"We are currently investing #294m on
OL,15,Ftraining new members of the workforce
OL,16,Fand continue to work with employers
OL,17,Fand unions to deliver the working
OL,18,Fenvironment and conditions our NHS
OL,19,Fstaff deserve."
