OL,7,FThe Welsh Conservatives said The Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment "had comprehensively failed
OL,9,Fto bring forward the substantial
OL,10,Fworkforce plan that the Welsh NHS
OL,11,Fneeds to serve the public."
OL,13,FResponding to the Audit Wales report,
OL,14,FDirector of the Welsh NHS
OL,15,FConfederation Darren Hughes said, "NHS
OL,16,Fleaders have long called for the Welsh
OL,17,FGovernment to invest in a fully costed
OL,18,FLong-Term Plan to deliver a
OL,19,Fsustainable NHS and social care
OL,20,Fworkforce if we are to meet the needs
OL,21,Fof the people of Wales"
