OL,7,F"Now more than ever we must strive to
OL,8,Fwork together across NHS and social
OL,9,Fcare boundaries to find long-term
OL,10,Fsolutions to recruitment and
OL,11,Fretention. But with the absence of a
OL,12,Flong overdue, government-led national
OL,13,Fplan for the sector and lack of
OL,14,Fclarity around system leadership
OL,15,Farrangements, health and social care
OL,16,Fleaders will struggle to deliver the
OL,17,Fworkforce needed to meet the needs of
OL,18,Fthe population."
